title: Spyder Auto Installation: 2011-14 Volkswagen Jetta Light Tube Projector Headlights
description: This video walkthrough is designed to demonstrate how to install a set of Spyder Auto projector headlights on any 2011-14 Volkswagen Jetta. This complete video tutorial covers the installation in depth from start to finish and offers helpful tips throughout to facilitate a successful installation.
